<topic id='element_episode_number.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: EPISODE NUMBER - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Format / Length</dt>
        <dd>n2</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_episode_number">EPISODE NUMBER</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_activity_identifier">ACTIVITY IDENTIFIER</xref>
 and is used to uniquely identify episodes, and is a sequence number for each 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_consultant_episode__hospital_provider_">Consultant Episode (Hospital Provider)</xref>
 in a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spell</xref>
. The first episode of each new 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spell</xref>
 (including re-admitted 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
) commences at 01.  </p>
  <p>
A known 
    <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_episode_number">EPISODE NUMBER</xref>
 can be between 01 to 87.  </p>
  <p>
For other 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Provider</xref>
 episodes, it is a sequence number for a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>
/
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 combination; or it is a sequence number for each 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_health_and_hiv_episode">Sexual Health and HIV Episode</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_episode_number">EPISODE NUMBER</xref>
 is used by the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/secondary_uses_service.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Secondary_Uses_Service</xref>
 to derive the 
    <b>
         <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/healthcare_resource_group.asp"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Healthcare_Resource_Group</xref>
      </b>
  
    <b>4</b>
. Failure to correctly populate this data element is likely to result in an incorrect 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/healthcare_resource_group.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Healthcare_Resource_Group</xref>
, usually associated with lower levels of healthcare resource.  </p>
  <p>
For further information, please refer to the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/services/secondary-uses-service-sus/payment-by-results-guidance"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Payment by Results Guidance</xref>
.  </p>


